Package functionality

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Assignment
    Assignment is the Class that handles a single assignment.It keeps track of whether the given assignment is a vacation, and if it is not, it keeps track of the test needing to be performed.
    Date
    Date is the class that handles time-related operations.
    Employee
    Employee is an extension of the Person class.This class extends the Person with functionality to store preferences of work and the training of the employee
    EmployeeList
    Employeelist is a class that collects Employee objects in a single List, for easy access.
    FileIO
    FileIO is a class that handles the File I/O, meaning it saves to, and loads from, a binary file containing all the Objects in the model.
    HTMLGenerator
    HTMLGenerator is a Class that takes a pre-written HTML file and changes the value within to output a schedule.
    Person
    Person is a Parent class to Employee and TeamLeader.
    Schedule
    Schedule is a class that handles the assignment of Assignment objects to Person (or its subclasses) objects.
    TeamLeader
    TeamLeader is a child class of Person, extending it with functionality to login to the system.
    Worksheet
    Worksheet is a class that stores the amount of people needed for a specific test.
